    Class
    Description
    AbstractPriorityQueue
    A skeletal implementation of the Priority Queue abstract data type.
    AbstractPriorityQueue.PQEntry
    PQEntry implements the Entry abstract data type for priority queues.
    AdaptablePriorityQueue
    The Adaptable Priority Queue abstract data type extends the behaviors of the Priority Queue abstract data type to allow removing arbitrary entries, updating an arbitrary entry's key (priority), and updating an arbitrary entry's value.
    HeapPriorityQueue
    A HeapPriorityQueue is an array-based min-heap implementation of the PriorityQueue abstract data type.
    PriorityQueue
    The Priority Queue abstract data type represents a collection of entries, where each entry consists of a 'key' that is mapped to a 'value'.
    PriorityQueue.Entry
    The Entry abstract data type defines behaviors for retrieving key and value data that are stored within the priority queue entry
